== 藥用價值 ==
{{medical}}
馬蹄大黃的根和莖是[[中醫|中醫]]常用作[[通便|通便]][[瀉火|瀉火]]的藥物，「药性峻利」<ref name=cihai />，「性大苦大寒」<ref name="huaxia">{{cite web |url=http://www.huaxia.com/hxjk/zhyx/zycs/2009/12/1690483.html |title=大黄的作用 |date=2009-12-23 |accessdate=2010-01-12 |publisher=华夏经纬网 |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110085122/http://www.huaxia.com/hxjk/zhyx/zycs/2009/12/1690483.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；此外，馬蹄大黃亦有活血的作用。這是由於馬蹄大黃含有[[蒽甙衍生物|蒽甙衍生物]]，其中以[[番泻甙|番泻甙]]的泻下作用最强，另还含有[[大黄鞣质|大黄鞣质]]及相关物质，如[[没食子酸|没食子酸]]、[[儿茶精|儿茶精]]和[[大黄四聚素|大黄四聚素]]等<ref name="huaxia" />。

在東南亞，有研究中醫藥的學者研究把藥用大黃用於治療[[乙型肝炎|乙型肝炎]]<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.ajph.org/cgi/content/abstract/92/10/1619 |title=Chinese Herbal Medicine and Interferon in the Treatment of Chronic Hepatitis B: A Meta-Analysis of Randomized, Controlled Trials |author=McCulloch et al. |volume=92 |issue=10 |pages=1619 |journal=American Journal of Public Health |access-date=2010-04-12 |archive-date=2008-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081029215427/http://www.ajph.org/cgi/content/abstract/92/10/1619 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

